.FoundFriendsContact
  if !authentication.id
    | Connect to Twitter to find friends on Are.na.

  else if authentication.id && contacts.models.length === 0
    | Could not find any friends on Are.na.

for user in contacts.models
  .FoundFriendsContact
    span.FoundFriendsContact__identifier
      .Avatar( data-initials= user.initials() )
        img(
          src= user.get('avatar_image').thumb
          alt= user.initials()
        )

      a( href="/#{user.get('slug')}", target='_blank' )
        = user.get('full_name')

    .FoundFriendsContact__follow.js-follow(
      data-type='User'
      data-id= user.id
    )
      //- Rendered client-side
